# 🩺 Pneumonia Detection using CNN

## 📌 Overview
This project aims to classify chest X-ray images into:
- Pneumonia
- Normal

## 🧠 Model Architecture
- Conv2D (32 filters)
- MaxPooling
- Conv2D (64 filters)
- MaxPooling
- Conv2D (128 filters)
- Flatten
- Dense Layer
- Output Layer (Sigmoid)

## ⚙️ Technologies Used
- Python
- TensorFlow / Keras
- NumPy

## 📊 Results
- Training Accuracy: ~90% (approx)
- Validation Accuracy: ~85% (approx)

## 🚀 Future Improvements
- Data Augmentation
- Transfer Learning (ResNet, VGG16)
- Hyperparameter tuning
